Cell["\<\
This notebook shows, metaphorically, how to find a \
2,000\[NoBreak]-\[NoBreak]dimensional needle in a \
2,000\[NoBreak]-\[NoBreak]dimensional haystack. Finding the needle takes \
fewer than 160,000 bisections more than 80% of the time. \
\>", "Text",
