Cell["\<\
The algorithm explored here is an abstraction of HPL (human-preference \
learning, https://openai.com/research/learning-from-human-preferences). The \
purpose of the abstraction is to estimate how many bisections \[LongDash] \
binary, subjective, human judgments \[LongDash] would be needed in a real \
robotic application, and thus to estimate the cost of HPL. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775402639959318*^9, 3.77540299308497*^9}, {
