  3.91182630428446*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"bef03be2-6a36-4198-bd58-\
2500076063d8"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In a real robotic application, HPL solicits a judgment by showing to the \
human two performances of two ",
 StyleBox["d",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "\[NoBreak]-\[NoBreak]dimensional controllers operating the same robot. The \
human subjectively picks the better of the two performances. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775402639959318*^9, 3.77540299308497*^9}, {
