Cell[TextData[{
 "The two controllers are chosen Gaussian-randomly within an appropriately \
sized ",
 StyleBox["d",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "\[NoBreak]-\[NoBreak]ball centered at the last best guess at the \
controller. The algorithm replaces the old best guess with the new best guess \
centered at a slightly smaller ",
 StyleBox["d",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "\[NoBreak]-\[NoBreak]ball, then generates two new random controllers and \
iterates. When the guess is good enough, subjectively, the algorithm halts. \
This technique is related to evolutionary strategies \
(https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evolution_strategy)."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775402639959318*^9, 3.77540299308497*^9}, {
