a786678c880d"],

Cell["\<\
In other work, we found, in fewer than 30 real human judgments, a \
16\[NoBreak]-\[NoBreak]dimensional LQR controller for balancing an inverted \
spherical pendulum \
(https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/pqd8b9f3p0q9sclfc76yy/\
SphericalPendulumIn28TrialsHighRes.mp4?rlkey=w970cjcwyhp76ozjsy6kasgc7&dl=0). \
This problem is analytically difficult. At the other extreme, the abstract \
method in this notebook found an oracular optimum in 5,000 dimensions in only \
1.3\[NonBreakingSpace]million judgments. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775402639959318*^9, 3.77540299308497*^9}, {
