39ce5761a5f3"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "A ",
 StyleBox["trial",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " is a sequence of judgments. The biggest trial in this notebook is in 2,000 \
dimensions with a maximum \"gas-tank\" of 160,000 judgments. It can take a \
couple of minutes to run on one core. We call the maximum number of \
judgments, say 160,000, a ",
 StyleBox["gas tank",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ", because we fail a search when it \"runs out of gas,\" that is, takes more \
judgments than we are willing to wait for. We express how long we're willing \
to wait by putting a number like 160,000 in the gas tank. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775402639959318*^9, 3.77540299308497*^9}, {
