Cell[TextData[{
 "REMARK: In other work, we ran a C++ version of this code, and found a 5,000\
\[NoBreak]-\[NoBreak]D optimum in 1.3\[NonBreakingSpace]million judgments out \
of a gas tank of 100 million. That was the biggest trial \
we\[CloseCurlyQuote]ve run so far with any software. It succeeded because of \
an educated guess at the correct \[CapitalDelta]. It took about three hours \
to run on one core. We do not know whether ",
 StyleBox["Mathematica",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " can do a trial that big. "
}], "Item",
