1829afd500be"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In this notebook, we do ",
 StyleBox["episodes",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " of 1600 trials in 16 ",
 StyleBox["rollouts",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " of 100 trials each. Each rollout tries a different decay \[CapitalDelta], \
16 in all. It takes ",
 StyleBox["Mathematica",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " about 6 hours on six cores in 64\[NonBreakingSpace]GB of memory for an \
episode of 1600 trials at 2,000 dimensions and a gas tank of 160,000. That's \
about a quarter billion ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["2000", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8c2f3eec-9d3f-47c1-a3f5-ca4e4f62c79b"],
 "\[NoBreak]-\[NoBreak]vectors, or half a trillion Gaussian samples. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775402639959318*^9, 3.77540299308497*^9}, {
