c4541701ede5"],

Cell["\<\
We settled on the following algorithm after previous correct but \
non-performant attempts. This algorithm has been tuned by trial-and-error.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.776083867246842*^9, 3.7760838879521723`*^9}, {
  3.776084050596422*^9, 3.776084079086537*^9}, {3.9115651112241077`*^9, 
