32c82911abba"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Inside the picture, we report the number of judgments, the result, and the \
final distance to the target. The unit ball around the origin is a light-gray \
disk. The white disk has radius ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Sigma]", "p"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "24cfb1ab-7eae-40e3-8856-9dee5e25cba0"],
 " centered on the target. Seeker radii start off as \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]cool\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] green and approach \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]hot\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] red as they approach the \
target."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.911575903981312*^9, 3.911575911575103*^9}, {
   3.911576023741024*^9, 3.911576063202272*^9}, {3.91159780618857*^9, 
