Cell["\<\
We now do a fast assessment in two dimensions. Looks like, with the death \
test off, we don\[CloseCurlyQuote]t get a higher \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Found\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] rate. As expected, we get no dead searches; all \
failures are wanderers.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.775491038655507*^9, 
  3.775491096808864*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ae4c7bb1-3720-4649-8ed4-\
4c06bb777eb1"],

